documents.name: true_doc1
documents.statement: On February 7, the WHO warned about the limited stock of PPE. That same day, the Trump administration announced it was sending 18 tons of masks, gowns and respirators to China.

documents.name: LOW
documents.statement: If I were not a Formula One pilot, I would be a football player.

documents.name: mostly-false_doc8
documents.statement: Says Joe Biden “was in charge of the H1N1 Swine Flu epidemic which killed thousands of people. The response was one of the worst on record. Our response is one of the best, with fast action of border closings & a 78% Approval Rating, the highest on record. His was lowest!”

documents.name: HIGH
documents.statement: Yes, We can!

documents.name: mostly-true_doc6
documents.statement: Says it was “unquestionably” not within his “legal authority” to postpone Illinois’ primary election by changing the date or shifting to vote-by-mail.

documents.statement: A video says that the Vatican confirmed that Pope Francis and two aides tested positive for coronavirus.
